data.description: Introducing this gorgeous and spacious home in the heart of Enumclaw. Enter inside to your large living room w/ vaulted ceilings and updated kitchen. Large main floor primary/bath, 3 additional bedrooms, full bath and den downstairs. Upstairs you will be amazed to find a SECOND primary suite. This gigantic bedroom has an attached room that could be used for anything your heart desires.  Across the hall you will see a large bonus room filled with natural light and a Mt Rainier view. Outside is a large backyard complete with dog-run, chicken coop, sheds and room for all your toys. RV parking, great schools, a quick walk to downtown shops. Seller coverage warranty and 1 year buyer warranty provided!
